Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.button

Interface ButtonService

All Superinterfaces:
TableInsertion
All Known Subinterfaces:
LinkService, TabService
All Known Implementing Classes:
ButtonServiceImpl, LinkServiceImpl, TabServiceImpl
public interface ButtonService extends TableInsertion
Provides service-level methods for interacting with button UI components.

This interface defines operations to click buttons and to check their enabled and visible states, delegating the actual interactions to specific implementations based on the configured ButtonComponentType.
